      <title>土耳其消费者通胀放缓速度创 2022 年以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/turkish-consumer-inflation-slows-at-sharpest-pace-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其7月份整体通胀率出现近两年来最大幅度下降，这一放缓主要是由于基数效应，而官员们可能因为关注更直接的价格风险而忽视了这一效应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/turkish-consumer-inflation-slows-at-sharpest-pace-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 07:02:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伯克希尔减持近一半股份后，苹果供应商股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/apple-supplier-stocks-slump-after-berkshire-nearly-halves-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伯克希尔哈撒韦公司 (Berkshire Hathaway Inc.) 几乎减持了苹果公司一半的股份，导致苹果公司供应商的股价暴跌。周一，苹果公司股价下跌，而与此同时，市场普遍出现抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/apple-supplier-stocks-slump-after-berkshire-nearly-halves-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 06:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>季风降雨充足，助力印度农民种植更多水稻和豆类</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/good-monsoon-rains-help-indian-farmers-plant-more-rice-pulses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受四个月的季风季节前半期降雨量高于平均水平的推动，印度农民扩大了水稻和豆类的种植面积。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/good-monsoon-rains-help-indian-farmers-plant-more-rice-pulses</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 06:25:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元升值加剧日本股市下跌，全球市场动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/intensifying-yen-rally-sinks-japan-stocks-rattles-global-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，日本金融市场动荡不安，日元兑美元汇率从 7 月低点反弹近 14%，股市跌入熊市。日本基准政府债券收益率创 20 多年来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/intensifying-yen-rally-sinks-japan-stocks-rattles-global-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 05:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚林吉特因资金流入和乐观情绪创下 2015 年以来最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/malaysian-ringgit-surges-most-since-2015-on-inflows-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场对马来西亚经济持乐观态度，外国资本将大量涌入，令吉汇率出现九年来最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/malaysian-ringgit-surges-most-since-2015-on-inflows-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 04:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国加大政策力度 服务业成为促进消费的主要力量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/china-services-expansion-picks-up-in-fresh-sign-of-momentum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国宣布了一项全面的计划，通过改善服务供给来刺激消费，寻求在制造业势头降温的情况下增强国内需求的亮点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/china-services-expansion-picks-up-in-fresh-sign-of-momentum</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:46:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>恐慌性抛售让亚洲股市迎来严峻的里程碑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/korea-s-kospi-index-plunges-takes-losses-from-july-peak-to-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美国经济进一步放缓以及日本股市持续暴跌，投资者风险偏好减弱，亚洲股市大幅下跌，而权重科技股的大幅抛售令情况更加糟糕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/korea-s-kospi-index-plunges-takes-losses-from-july-peak-to-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:20:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>信心崩塌，日本股市跌入熊市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japan-s-stock-rout-enters-third-day-with-nikkei-in-bear-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者信心消失，日本东证股价指数从上月创下的历史高点下跌了 24%，日经 225 股票平均指数以日元计算出现最大单日跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japan-s-stock-rout-enters-third-day-with-nikkei-in-bear-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:18:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
