    <item>
      <title>油价从七个月低点回落，因股市暴跌抵消了伊朗风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东地区紧张局势加剧，金融市场普遍出现抛售，交易员担心伊朗可能对以色列采取报复性打击，油价从七个月来的最低收盘价延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 23:10:42 GMT</pubDate>
